# Task 1: Term Deposit Subscription Prediction (Bank Marketing)

## Objective
Predict whether a bank customer will subscribe to a term deposit as a result of a marketing campaign.

## Dataset
Bank Marketing Dataset (UCI Machine Learning Repository)

## Approach
- Loaded and explored the dataset (missing values, distributions, target balance)
- Preprocessed data using:
  - OneHotEncoding for categorical features
  - Scaling numeric features (for Logistic Regression)
- Trained:
  - Logistic Regression (baseline)
  - Random Forest (nonlinear)
- Evaluated models using:
  - Confusion Matrix
  - F1-score
  - ROC Curve + ROC-AUC
- Used SHAP to:
  - Explain global feature importance
  - Explain at least 5 individual predictions

